    "summary": "The user expresses existential nihilism and despair after contemplating the vastness of space, questioning the point of continuing to live. The assistant responds by validating the user's feeling of cosmic insignificance but ultimately encourages the user to find meaning in their own existence and emphasizes the value of being alive.",
